OL,5,Csalary
OL,7,FManchester City must pay former
OL,8,Ffootballer Benjamin Mendy the majority
OL,9,Fof his #11.5 million unpaid salary
OL,10,Fwithheld from him after he was charged
OL,11,Fwith sex offences, an employment
OL,12,Ftribunal has ruled.
OL,14,FThe 30-year-old's #500,000-per-month
OL,15,Fwage was withheld by the club after he
OL,16,Fwas charged in 2021. The French
OL,17,Finternational and World Cup winner was
OL,18,Fsubsequently cleared of all charges
OL,19,Fafter two trials.
