OL,5,Csalary
OL,7,FEmployment Judge Joanne Dunlop said
OL,8,Fshe had concluded that Mr Mendy is
OL,9,F"entitled to recover some, but not all
OL,10,Fof the sums claimed", following a
OL,11,Fhearing at Manchester Employment
OL,12,FTribunal.
OL,14,FMs Dunlop said that while Mr Mendy was
OL,15,Fnot in custody, he was "ready and
OL,16,Fwilling" to work and was "prevented
OL,17,Ffrom doing so which were unavoidable
OL,18,For involuntary on his part".
