OL,7,F"In those circumstances, and absent
OL,8,Fany authorisation in the contract for
OL,9,Fthe employer to withhold pay, he was
OL,10,Fentitled to be paid," she said.
OL,12,FMendy said he is "delighted" after
OL,13,FCity was ordered to pay him around
OL,14,F#8.5 million and called on the club to
OL,15,Fdo the "honourable thing" and pay up
OL,16,Fquickly so he can move on with his
OL,17,Flife.
