OL,7,FIn a statement, Mr Mendy thanked his
OL,8,Flawyers and said: "Having had to wait
OL,9,Ffor three years for my wages, I am
OL,10,Fdelighted with the decision and
OL,11,Fsincerely hope that the club will now
OL,12,Fdo the honourable thing and pay the
OL,13,Foutstanding amounts, as well as the
OL,14,Fother amounts promised to me under the
OL,15,Fcontract, without further delay, so I
OL,16,Fcan finally put this difficult part of
OL,17,Fmy life behind me."
