OL,7,FThe tribunal previous heard Mendy, who
OL,8,Fnow plays for French Ligue 2 club
OL,9,FLorient, "struggled to pay child
OL,10,Fsupport" after Manchester City stopped
OL,11,Fpaying him, with fellow footballers
OL,12,FRaheem Sterling, Bernardo Silva and
OL,13,FRiyad Mahrez lending him money.
OL,15,FCourt documents said Mendy "very
OL,16,Fquickly ran out of money" and had to
OL,17,Fsell his Cheshire mansion to cover
OL,18,Flegal fees, bills and child support
OL,19,Fpayments after his wages were withheld.
