OL,7,F"I struggled to pay my child support,
OL,8,FI felt awful," the footballer said in
OL,9,Fa witness statement.
OL,11,FMendy said his agent, Meissa N'diaye,
OL,12,Fpaid towards his legal fees, while
OL,13,Fteam-mates including England
OL,14,Finternational Sterling offered
OL,15,F"financial support".
OL,17,F"Raheem Sterling, Bernardo Silva and
OL,18,FRiyad Mahrez all lent me money to help
OL,19,Fme try and pay my legal fees and
OL,20,Fsupport my family," he said in his
OL,21,Fwitness statement.
