OL,7,FThe tribunal heard he enjoyed
OL,8,Fpartying, and was held in custody
OL,9,Fbetween August 2021 and January 2022,
OL,10,Fand again between December 2022 and
OL,11,FJanuary 2023 after he breached his
OL,12,Fbail conditions by hosting and
OL,13,Fattending multiple parties.
