OL,7,FMendy, appearing via videolink at the
OL,8,Ftwo-day hearing in October, told the
OL,9,Ftribunal he and his agent N'diaye had
OL,10,Fbeen assured by City's then Chief
OL,11,FFootball Operating officer Omar
OL,12,FBerrada that he would receive his
OL,13,Funpaid wages once he had been cleared
OL,14,Fof the charges.
OL,16,FThe footballer sent Berrada a WhatsApp
OL,17,Fmessage in November 2022, asking if he
OL,18,Fcould confirm in writing that the
OL,19,Fwages would be paid, the tribunal
OL,20,Fheard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
