OL,7,FBut Berrada did not reply to the
OL,8,Fmessage and denied ever having made
OL,9,Fsuch an assurance.
OL,11,FAfter his acquittal, Mendy sent an
OL,12,Femail to Khaldoon Al Mubarak, the
OL,13,Fchief executive of City, but again
OL,14,Freceived no response.
