OL,7,FThe club continued paying Mendy
OL,8,Ffollowing his first arrest in November
OL,9,F2020, but argued they did not have to
OL,10,Fcarry on doing so later because his
OL,11,Fbail conditions and Football
OL,12,FAssociation suspension meant he was
OL,13,Fnot able to perform his duties as a
OL,14,Fplayer.
OL,16,FSean Jones KC, representing the club,
OL,17,Ftold the tribunal the player only had
OL,18,Fhimself to blame for not being paid.
