OL,7,FHe said Mendy's womanising, partying
OL,8,Fduring the Covid lockdown, and
OL,9,Fbreaking bail conditions led to his
OL,10,Farrest and stay in jail.
OL,12,FMendy, Mr Jones told the tribunal,
OL,13,Fthought he could "ignore all the
OL,14,Frules", resulting in him being unable
OL,15,Fto train and play for Man City, but
OL,16,Fclaimed it should not affect his
OL,17,Fentitlement to pay.
