OL,7,FHis "luck ran out" finally in August
OL,8,F2021 when, following a further
OL,9,Fallegation, he was charged with
OL,10,Foffences, a judge remanded him in
OL,11,Fcustody and the club stopped paying
OL,12,Fhim.
OL,14,FMendy was then unable to train or play
OL,15,Ffor Man City ` his "core duties" as an
OL,16,Femployee of the club, who stopped his
OL,17,Fwages.
OL,19,FBut Nick De Marco KC, representing
OL,20,FMendy, told the tribunal the case was
OL,21,Fnot about the footballer's lifestyle.
