OL,7,F"He partied too much and too often.
OL,8,FVery often with other high-profile
OL,9,Fmembers of Manchester City's team," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"As a result of allegations that
OL,13,Fturned out to have all been dismissed,
OL,14,Fhe spent over four months in custody `
OL,15,Ftime he can never get back."
