OL,7,FMendy was found not guilty of six
OL,8,Fcounts of rape and one count of sexual
OL,9,Fassault in January 2023, but the same
OL,10,Fjury could not reach a verdict on
OL,11,Fanother count of rape and one count of
OL,12,Fattempted rape.
OL,14,FIt led to a retrial after which Mendy
OL,15,Fwas found not guilty of one charge of
OL,16,Frape and one charge of attempted rape.
