OL,7,FMendy's claim covered a 22-month
OL,8,Fperiod, five of which were when he was
OL,9,Fin custody for breaching bail
OL,10,Fconditions and therefore not entitled
OL,11,Fto pay, the judge ruled.
OL,13,FThis leaves him with around #8.5
OL,14,Fmillion owed, though the exact amount
OL,15,Fis yet to be agreed by his lawyers and
OL,16,FManchester City.
